metadata.description:
MIAMI FREESTYLE (ft. Aly, Tarot, Elle Symone, Early, & TK | prod. AbJo)

MIAMI FREESTYLE is our Genesis Music NFT release. This song is the first success of our first-ever collaborative artist camp at Art Basel in Miami, Florida. This camp featured over 50 artists of various walks of life collaborating in spontaneous fashion. 

CAMPFIRE S1 is a curated collection of songs voted on by the CAMPFIRE community.

Produced by Abjo.

Mixed & Mastered by Pete Rango.

Artwork by Karey & TK.
